



to generate the initial condition:
```
galaxy_ic  2   -1. -1.  0. 0. 0.5 0.25 0.      0.1 1.035 0 16 128 2048 4. 4. 100 1000 1. \
                1. -1.  0. 0. 0.5 0.25 3.1415  0.1 1.035 0 16 128 2048 4. -4. 100 1000 1. \
                8 ./ic
```

to plot the initial condition:
```
./plot_ic ./ic > ic.py; python3 ic.py
```
